snippet.title: MahaShivRatri 2025 – Livestream with Sadhguru | 26 Feb, 6 PM - 27 Feb, 6 AM IST
snippet.description:
Celebrate Mahashivratri 2025 with Sadhguru on 26 February 2025, starting at 6 PM IST/12:30 PM GMT.

On Mahashivratri night, there is a powerful natural upsurge of energy in the human system. It is enormously beneficial for one’s physical and spiritual wellbeing to stay awake and aware in a vertical posture throughout the night.

This year, Sadhguru will be offering initiation into the powerful Mahamantra (Aum Namah Shivaya) at midnight.

This Mahashivratri, contribute towards supporting Mahashivratri activities and Maha Annadanam (the sacred offering of food) to thousands of devotees. Your contribution, small or large, will make a big difference! Donate Now: https://sadhguru.co/annam

Join Sadhguru for the powerful Pancha Bhuta Kriya online on the auspicious night of Mahashivratri. Experience this powerful process that brings the body and mind to a vibrant state of health and wellbeing by purifying the five elements within the human system.
Register Now : https://sadhguru.co/pbk-yt

Police finally catches hold of the scammers. Everyone gathers at Bhide's house to inform him that he will get back all his money. Meanwhile, Popatlal tells Tapu and his friends about a celebrity who will be coming to meet them all.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 587
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Click Here To Watch More Episodes Of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:

snippet.title: HACKER OR WHAT! | JONATHAN IS BACK | BGMI
snippet.description:
Hey Guys, I’m Jonathan Amaral, better known as Jonathan Gaming, a professional BGMI esports athlete and streamer.

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I’ve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I’ve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

Official Red Bull Athlete 🪽
MVP of PMCO Fall Split 2019 South Asia 🏅
MVP of PUBG Mobile World League 2020 🌍
MVP of BGMS SEASON 1 2022 🏆
Ranked among the Top Esports Mobile Players in the World 🔥

snippet.title: Badshah - Dear Aditya (Official Music Video) | Hiten
snippet.description:
A Letter To Myself

Audio Credits :
➟ Performed By Badshah
➟ Lyrics By Badshah
➟ Composed By  Badshah
➟ Music Produced By Hiten 
➟ Mixed & Mastered By Hiten
➟ Chorus Performed by Vaidik Dawale, Aanya Jain, Veda Mahajan & Advik Kasbe

Lyrics: 
Kaisa hai kya haal hai kya chal raha hai
Gaane vaane sun raha hai ya padh raha hai
Jitna marzi rishtedar tere peeche padein dekh
Dariyo na tu sapne dekh aur bade dekh
Ye jaankar tu aaj bada dang hoga
Ke pandran saal mein in sabka mooh band hoga
Jin teacheron ko tujhse zaraa bhi ummeed nai thi un saare teacheron ki naak mein dum

Papa ka thoda dhyaan rakh unka dil kamzor hai
Tere aas paas aadhe se zaada bande chor hain
Dost kam rakhiyo circle usse chota
Paisa boht aane wala hai wallet mota rakhiyo
Maa baap ke siva koi saga nai milega
Sukoon ghar ko chod kisi jagah nai milega
Jisko pyaar tu karega dil wo tera todegi
Kisi paise wale ke liye wo tujhe chodegi
Ek dedh hafta rona, man kare to chillana
Lekin fir chup chaap wapas music pe lag jaana
Uski yaad mein koi sad songs nahi banaiyo
Log waise hi boht rote hain tu party karaiyo

Koi dedh chaal chale to tu dhai samajhna
Par jo pakde tera hath use bhai samajhna
Par kain baar hath deke hathon ki lakeerein le jaate hain log tab hathon ki safai samajhna
Hateron ka dil dekh dehelte rahega
Shuru jaise marzi karaa ant keher se karega
2 kamron ke ghar mein tha janma tu tujhe pata nahi tu ek din kitne bade mahal mein rahega
Maa khush hogi lekin papa khush ni rahenge
Unka man hai tu IAS bane par push ni karenge
Log teri lagataar kaamyaabi dekh bore hoke hate karenge par mooh pe kuch ni kahenge

Haan…. tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga
Naam badshah aur sabko tera naam yaad hoga
Haan…. Tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga

Chaltre reh rukh nai
Khone ko kuch nai
Humko tujhe pe hai yakeen
Humko khudh pe hai yakeen
Rakhna mat tu sabr
Cheen le 
Kood kar 
Aasmaan aur Zameen 
Humko tujh pe hai yakeen

Behkaave mein aake tu sidein switch nai karna
Fame ke chakkar mein kisiko diss nai karna
Khoob mehnat karna sirf wish nai karna
Aur jab saamne nishaana ho to miss nai karna
tujhe ladna hi hoga
Chahe kat jayen taangein aage badhna hi hog
Yaad rakh fame ek kiraaye ka makaan hai
Ek din tujhe ise khali karna hi hoga
jaam na sharaab lena, pyaar behisaab dena
Mooh kam kholiyo tu Kaam se jawaab dena
Banda tujhse kya chahe aankhon se bhaanp lena
Jo karega wo bharega khud ko na paap dena

Chaltre reh rukh nai
Khone ko kuch nai
Humko tujhe pe hai yakeen
Humko khudh pe hai yakeen
Rakhna mat tu sabr
Cheen le 
Kood kar 
Aasmaan aur Zameen 
Humko tujh pe hai yakeen

Haan…. tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga
Naam badshah aur sabko tera naam yaad hoga
Haan…. Tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga

Khoob mehnat karna sirf wish nai karna
Aur jab saamne nishaana ho to miss nai karna
tujhe ladna hi hoga
Chahe kat jayen taangein aage badhna hi hog
Yaad rakh fame ek kiraaye ka makaan hai
Ek din tujhe ise khali karna hi hoga
jaam na sharaab lena, pyaar behisaab dena
Mooh kam kholiyo tu Kaam se jawaab dena
Banda tujhse kya chahe aankhon se bhaanp lena
Jo karega wo bharega khud ko na paap dena

Chaltre reh rukh nai
Khone ko kuch nai
Humko tujhe pe hai yakeen
Humko khudh pe hai yakeen
Rakhna mat tu sabr
Cheen le 
Kood kar 
Aasmaan aur Zameen 
Humko tujh pe hai yakeen

Haan…. tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga
Naam badshah aur sabko tera naam yaad hoga
Haan…. Tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga

snippet.title: The Bhootnii - Announcement | Sanjay D, Mouni R, Sunny, Palak, Nick | Sidhaant S | Deepak M | 18 Apr
snippet.description:
Get ready for a rollercoaster of horror, romance, and comedy like never before! Presenting "The Bhootnii", where love, laughter and supernatural thrills come together in the most unexpected way! 👻💘🤣

Starring the legendary Sanjay Dutt, the stunning Mouni Roy, the charming Sunny Singh, the talented Palak Tiwari, the hilarious Asif Khan, and the quirky BeYounik, this film is packed with spine-tingling moments, hilarious twists, and a whole lot of romance! 💀❤️✨

🎬The Bhootnii is set to hit theaters on 18th April 2025.

Credits : 
⭐ cast : Sanjay Dutt, Mouni Roy, Sunny Singh, Palak Tiwari, Asif Khan, BeYounik & Others
Written & Directed by : Sidhaant Sachdev
Produced by : Deepak Mukut & Sanjay Dutt
Co-Produced by : Hunar Mukut & Maanayata Dutt
Associate Producer : Johari Tailor
DOP : Santosh Thundiyil ISC

Executive Producer: Mehboob Ansari & Pradeep Singh

Costume Designer- Priyanka Mundada 
Sanjay Dutt’s Costume- Anna Singh & Navin Shetty
VFX : Redifine 
VFX Supervisor - Govardhan Vigraham
Associate Director : Rishabh Rishi Kumar 
Music : ICONYK, Shabbir Ahmed, Mukund Suryawanshi (Jam8)
Creative Director : Manoj Tiwari & Rishi Anand
CEO (TDM) : Gaurav Dubey
CEO & Business Head (SRE) : Shailendra Mandowara 
Digital Mrkt. Manager (SRE) : Ajay S Singh
Production Team (SRE) : Lucky Tomar, Shivam Rao
Banner : Soham Rockstar Entertainment & Three Dimension Motion Pictures

snippet.title: Kollagottinadhiro -Lyrical|Hari Hara Veera Mallu|PSPK|Nidhhi|MM Keeravaani |AM Rathnam|Jyothi Krisna
snippet.description:
Experience our folksy foot-tapping number " Kollagottinadhiro" from 'Hari Hara Veera Mallu (Telugu)'  🎶🔥 Featuring Power Star Pawan Kalyan, Nidhhi Agerwal, and Bobby Deol, this foot-tapping track is composed by Oscar winner MM Keeravaani and directed by Jyothi Krisna & Krish Jagarlamudi.

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Telugu, Subscribe on the below link
https://youtube.com/TipsTelugu

Song Details : 
Song Name: Kollagottinadhiro
Music Director: M. M. Keeravaani 
Lyricist: Chandrabose 
Singers: Mangli, Rahul Sipligunj , Ramya Behara, Yamini Ghantasala. 
Chorus : Lokeshwar Edara, Sai Charan, Arun kaundinya, Airaa Udupi , Lipsika Bhashyam, Vaish
Programmed, Mixed and Mastered by : Jeevan Babu 
Recording Studio: JB Studios 
Co-ordinator: A N Basha

Starring: Pawan Kalyan, Nidhhi Agerwal, Bobby Deol & others.

Produced by: A. Dayakar Rao
Presents: AM Rathnam 
Banner: Mega Surya Production
Music On: Tips Music Limited (Tips Telugu)

Lyrics : 
Kora Kora Meesalatho, Kodama Kodama Adugulatho 
Kontey Kontey Chenukulatho, Kolimilanti Magatimitho Sarasara Vacchinaadu Chicchara Pidugantivaadu 
Edo Edo Thalachinaadu Evvarino Vethikinaadu 
Evaranta… Evaranta… Evarevaranta
Evaranta Evaranta Evarevarevarevaranta

Kondapalli Endi Bomma 
Kola Kallatho Chusindamma Teeyateeyani Teynelakomma
Teeyani Teraley Teesindamma
Vajrala Jilugulunna 
Rathnala Yelugulunna Kempulla Ompulunna Mohareela Merupulunna
Naa Paidi Gundeylona Edi Puttinchi 
Mariginchi Mariginchi Kariginchi Kariginchi

Kollagottinaadiro…..Kollagottinaadiro 
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro
Kollagottinaadiro…..Kollagottinaadiro 
Mulleygattinaadiro…Mulleygattinaadiro…

Ayyayyayyo….…Aa Chinnadi 
Inkemi Chesindayyo. 
Ayyayyayyo...Aa Kurradi Aa Mantram Esindayyo..

Kannulaloni Kaatuka Megham 
Seekati Naapai Silikindey 
Maatalathoney Melikeysindi 
Marmam Edo Daasindey
Aadavaallu Manasu Adavilantidani 
Eragani Santodiva
Antha Amayakudiva
Padusupilla Teeru Pattusikkadani Pasigattalenodiva 
Votti Shontikommuva…
Letha Ennapoosava…..
Are Meesala Roshala Monaganni Pattesi 
Pasivanni Chesesi Pasaredo Poosesi…
Kollagottinaadiro
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro 
Kollagottinaadiro….
Mulleygattinaadiro…Mulleygattinaadiro…

Oopiriloni Aaviripavanaaley 
Viriviga Lekhaley Visireney
Uppena Laaga Pongey Pourushamey 
Sogasuku Sankela Veseyney
Cheekuchintha Leni Vaadi Chittam Dochavey Parahushaar Poragadni Paagal Chesavey Daaredayina Davvedayina Needayi Untaney Pereydaina Teeredayina Penimiti Antaney Addeddedde….
Kollagottinaadiro….
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro 
Kollagottinaadiro Mulleygattinaadiro…

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for the greatest adventure ever built. ⛏️ Tickets are on sale NOW for #MinecraftMovie – only in theaters April 4. https://www.fandango.com/MinecraftMovie

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, “A Minecraft Movie,” directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time. 

The film also stars Emma Myers (“Wednesday”), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (“The Color Purple”), Sebastian Hansen (“Just Mercy, “Lisey’s Story”), with Jennifer Coolidge. 

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn’t just help you craft, it’s essential to one’s survival! Four misfits—Garrett “The Garbage Man” Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)—find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they’ll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative…the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (“Ninety-Five Senses,” “Nacho Libre”) directed from a screenplay by Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer and Neil Widener & Gavin James and Chris Galletta, story by Allison Schroeder and Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, based on the Minecraft video game. Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Ólafsson and Vu Bui produced, and Todd Hallowell, Jay Ashenfelter, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza and Jon Spaihts executive produced. 

The director’s creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (“127 Hours,” “Transformers: Rise of the Beasts”), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (“The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,” “The Meg”), editor James Thomas (“Pokémon: Detective Pikachu”, the “Borat” films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (“The Jungle Book,” “The Batman”), and costume designer Amanda Neale (“The Meg,” “What We Do in the Shadows”). Casting is by Rachel Tenner. The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (“Thor: Ragnarok,” the “LEGO®” movies). 

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Mojang Studios Production, A Jared Hess Film, “A Minecraft Movie.” The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4332 - Bapuji Tapu ki Shadi Karwa ke Hi Manenge?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Bapuji ki Jidd | Tapu ki Shadi | Gokuldham Society | Sonu ki shadi

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

Produced By: Neela Asit Modi, Asit Kumarr Modi

For Aloo Lacche:
• Potato (आलू) - 4
• Water (पानी) - For Boiling
• Rock Salt(सेंधा नमक) - Some
• Water Chestnut Flour (सिंघाड़ा आटा) - 4 Tbsp

For Filling
• Grated Ginger (अदरक) - 1 Tbsp
• Coriander leaves(धनिया पत्ती) - 1-2  Tbsp
• Cashew Nuts (काजू) – 1 Tbsp
• Raisins (किशमिश) - 1 Tbsp
• Cottage Cheese/Paneer (पनीर) -  100 Gram
• Salt (नमक) - 1/2 Tsp
• Black Pepper Powder (काली मिर्च) - 1/2 Tsp
• Green Chili (हरी मिर्च) - 2-3
• Oil/Ghee (तेल/घी) - For Frying

For Serving:
• Whisked Curd (फेंटा हुआ दही)
• Green Chutney (हरी चटनी)
• Sweet Chutney (मीठी चटनी)
• Pomagranate Seeds (अनार के दाने)
• Coriander leaves (धनिया पत्ती)
• Roasted Cumin Powder (जीरा पाउडर)

snippet.title: Son of Sreenivasan Roast | Love Under Construction | Dhyan | Neeraj | Aju | Vishnu | Feb 28th
snippet.description:
Brace yourselves for the ultimate roast interview! Dhyan Sreenivasan takes the hot seat as the host of Son of Sreenivasan Roast, where he gets hilariously grilled alongside his guests—Neeraj Madhav, Aju Varghese, and Vishnu Raghav. Expect witty comebacks, savage burns, and non-stop laughter as they dish out jokes, share behind-the-scenes fun, and promote their upcoming web series Love Under Construction, streaming on JioHotstar from February 28.

Don't miss this riotous episode full of fun, banter, and unexpected twists!

Episode 4331: Raja Mastana's Prediction
--------------------------------------------------------
Raja Mastana visits Gokuldham Society as part of Bhide's plan, shocking Tapu and Sonu with his prediction about their marriage. How will they get out of this?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Bhide Ka Surprise | Bhide dega Jhatka | Gokuldham Society

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

Mehshar Digitally Presented by Nestle Bunyad

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated project, Mehshar, reunites the beloved on-screen duo of Imran Abbas and Neelam Muneer in a tale of love that promises to leave a mark on the viewers!

In Mehshar, love meets sacrifice as it follows the journey of a person who adores someone whose ambitions surpass all, leaving love behind. This is a story where love is selfless and giving is what matters most.

The story revolves around Abdur Rehman and Aima, cousins bound by a twist of fate. Their journey is not just about love, it’s about the emotions and sacrifices that truly make their bond special.

Is Abdur Rehman and Aima’s love destined to last forever, or will tragedy destroy it? Will their sacrifices and emotions elevate love to new heights? Will ambitions overpower love in this tale?

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Bajjo Episode 66 - [Eng Sub] - Javeria Saud - Arez Ahmed - Suqaynah Khan - 27th February 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Bajjo is a heartfelt family drama that blends light-hearted moments with emotional turbulence. It portrays the struggles and conflicts of a middle-class household, where differences and arguments often take center stage.
Musarrat, fondly called Bajjo, is the eldest sibling, known for her sharp tongue and bitter demeanor. Her unmarried status fuels her frustration, leading to threats of drastic actions if anyone weds before her. This turmoil unsettles the entire family, but when a proposal finally comes her way, it brings its own set of challenges.
Will Bajjo ever find her match? Can her attitude change, or will it continue to cause problems for her family? Is her family’s patience running out, or will they stand by her despite her flaws? Can Bajjo overcome her struggles?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Mazhar Moin
Writer: Javeria Saud

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: When You Have a Crush On Your Boss - Part 2| Ft. Keshav Sadhna,  Anjum Khan, Reshham Sahaani
snippet.description:
#filtercopy #officeromace #crush

Kaisa laga Part 2? Comments mein batao 😋

Ever felt that sudden wave of... something... when your boss is around? We're diving into that feeling! Yeah, we've all been there! In this super fun video, we're diving straight into the hilarious mess of having a crush on your boss! 😅

We've packed it with all the relatable moments of office romance, the kind where you're constantly wondering, "Is this real, or am I just imagining things?" 🤷‍♀️ From accidental touches during team meetings to trying to decipher those "friendly" smiles that might mean something more, every moment is a minefield of mixed signals.You know that feeling when you're trying to act cool, but your heart is doing a bhangra inside? 

This video is for anyone who's ever had a crush on their boss, found themselves overthinking every little interaction, or just loves a good dose of desi comedy. Get ready for some serious LOL moments, a few cringes (because, let's be honest, we've all been there!), and a whole lot of "OMG, same!" vibes.

So settle in, and get ready to dive into the chaos of office romance. Don't forget to LIKE, COMMENT, and SUBSCRIBE for more hilarious content! And share your own office crush stories in the comments – we want to hear all the juicy details! 😉 Let's see if your office crush stories are as crazy as ours!

Don't forget to follow us for more fun content!

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/filtercopy
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/FilterCopy/

snippet.title: Shiv Aarti Anuradha Paudwal | Jai Shiv Omkara | Shiv Aarti | Shiv Ji Ki Aarti | ॐ जय शिव ओंकारा
snippet.description:
Shiv Aarti Anuradha Paudwal | Jai Shiv Omkara | Shiv Aarti | Shiv Ji Ki Aarti | ॐ जय शिव ओंकारा
Song - Jai Shiv Omkara
Singer - Anuradha Paudwal
Music Director: Dr. Sanjayraj Gaurinandan (SRG)
Lyrics: Traditional

अपने दिन को सकारात्मक ऊर्जा से भरने के लिए सब्सक्राइब कीजिये और अपने मित्र परिवार के साथ शेर कीजिये| 
🔔 SUBSCRIBE NOW: 
https://www.youtube.com/@ShemarooBhakti

!! ॐ जय शिव ओंकारा की आरती - Om Jai Shiv Omkara Lyrics in Hindi !!
.
ओम जय शिव ओंकारा, स्वामी जय शिव ओंकारा।
ब्रह्मा, विष्णु, सदाशिव, अर्द्धांगी धारा॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
एकानन चतुरानन पञ्चानन राजे।
हंसासन गरूड़ासन वृषवाहन साजे॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
दो भुज चार चतुर्भुज दसभुज अति सोहे।
त्रिगुण रूप निरखत त्रिभुवन जन मोहे॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
अक्षमाला वनमाला मुण्डमालाधारी।
त्रिपुरारी कंसारी कर माला धारी॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
श्वेताम्बर पीताम्बर बाघंबर अंगे।
सनकादिक गरुड़ादिक भूतादिक संगे॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
कर के मध्य कमण्डल चक्र त्रिशूलधारी।
जगकर्ता जगभर्ता जगसंहारकर्ता॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
ब्रह्मा विष्णु सदाशिव जानत अविवेका।
प्रणवाक्षर के मध्ये ये तीनों एका॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
पर्वत सोहैं पार्वती, शंकर कैलासा।
भांग धतूरे का भोजन, भस्मी में वासा॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
जटा में गंग बहत है, गल मुण्डन माला।
शेष नाग लिपटावत, ओढ़त मृगछाला॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
काशी में विराजे विश्वनाथ, नन्दी ब्रह्मचारी।
नित उठ दर्शन पावत, महिमा अति भारी॥ ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥
त्रिगुणस्वामी जी की आरति जो कोइ नर गावे।
कहत शिवानन्द स्वामी, मनवान्छित फल पावे॥
ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥ स्वामी ओम जय शिव ओंकारा॥

Shiv Aarti & Bhajans

https://youtu.be/E1I_05xu-ro
https://youtu.be/Eef79MK4bSA
https://youtu.be/KjuxFnWdYpk
https://youtu.be/FkqhOr_U90E
https://youtu.be/JN_EvHnCpvY
